Question-20_key1: Write a function named license_checker that checks drivers speed, this function needs to take a parameter named speed.
Question-20_key2: If speed is less than 70 then prints “ok”.
Question-20_key3: If speed is more than 70 then function gives 1 point for each 5 km (this won’t count 70).
Question-20_key4: Example: for speed 80 the points should be “points:2” .
Question-20_key5: If the driver got more than 12 points, the function has to give “License suspended” .
